{"tid":2031142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒點解聽日嗌香港獨立係咁重要！","createTime":"2020-05-23T07:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T17:30:06.000Z","uid":302,"like":66,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b143e9c8f8f2ba91f1642cfdde0f39ace9524580","tid":2031142,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:58:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為我地要建構民族自強既意識形態！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人 就好似主權寄生族<br />\n<br />\n一邊寄生中國 跪求阿爺施捨自由<br />\n一邊寄生美國 祈求國際開聲援助<br />\n<br />\n但係無論對中國定國際 香港只係一處搵錢既地方<br />\n<br />\n香港人身份？Who fucking cares?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人話香港獨立騎劫反惡歌法<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 係五大訴求騎劫左香港獨立一整年<br />\n<br />\n今日反放中 聽日反惡歌法 後日反國安法 之後反23條 然後再有反社會評分 反家居監控 反轉再反轉<br />\n<br />\n香港人 你想反到幾時？<br />\n<br />\n只有我地香港人 拎返我地既話語權 <br />\n我地既後代 先身身世世 可以享受自由既空氣<br />\n<br />\n無論我地最終留係本土掙扎到獨立 <br />\n還是選擇海外建國<br />\n<br />\n目的都只有一個 就係香港人執政！<br />\n<br />\n猶太人可以係依度打交打到落以色列去做渣fit人，我香港都可以！<br />\n<br />\n只有我地香港人自己 先可以拯救我地既香港民族<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民族自強 香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n香港人 建國！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5583f5cf173c505200fff2a1a0114cdf6fcc2e3","tid":2031142,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"民族自強 香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n香港人 建國！"},{"pid":"b02cebf9245ec0ae335b9de9e0404ce521cfb827","tid":2031142,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">生生世世 世世代代</span>"},{"pid":"29a03172d23a2195b52cc740eb82d14f19ab5d0f","tid":2031142,"uid":200666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:01:27.000Z","msg":"民族自強"},{"pid":"f7eb411d1cef603fcb0352a2fc08a4b67d8fce42","tid":2031142,"uid":200666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"cac3d8c908b87d7f1e00ad88c6c7f835cd7b2543","tid":2031142,"uid":302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:02:29.000Z","msg":"今日唔過國安法 聽日都會過23條<br />\n<br />\n只係時間既問題 <br />\n<br />\n但係大家一日都唔係要自己渣莊既信念醒覺<br />\n<br />\n我地一世都只會係no body"},{"pid":"85cdf4e6de9177ad54fc338133aa50b8e10ff87e","tid":2031142,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"點解柒婆係習總面前成個奴才咁樣<br />\n<br />\n李胃鯨入中聯辦成隻狗樣頭dup dup?"},{"pid":"799af7822843148cf1c0777e682d3a8abee7e8c4","tid":2031142,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得寧為玉碎 不為瓦全？<br />\n<br />\n仲要為左乞求少少既自由 連香港獨立都唔敢叫？"},{"pid":"60e2fc89a5e5f30c90413d5fcc32d8e73216b875","tid":2031142,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"One Nation<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faecc0f596e20769aa06952467be5ee399389c0d","tid":2031142,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60e2fc89a5e5f30c90413d5fcc32d8e73216b875","tid":2031142,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"One Nation<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:05:23.000Z","msg":"One Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"f80670dadb769346f23bcaf1a10409858322e8d8","tid":2031142,"uid":187201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:07:12.000Z","msg":"我地唔只係反對一條條例，係反對整個政權，<br />\n因為只要中共同港共繼續掌權，<br />\n只會有更多惡法出現，只會有更多人被壓逼，被自殺被浮屍<br />\n<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立！<br />\n香港人執政！香港人建國！"},{"pid":"8160934eb113d6aec25064b91917da722c02d288","tid":2031142,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"蔡英文： 「國家的存在不是為了能稱霸世界，而是讓它的國民活得有尊嚴！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2030052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2030052</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a46e32bbf0c65226ad6921b37c1fcf41cf7a65e","tid":2031142,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo